    <item>
      <title>摇摆州法官驳回共和党对 2024 年海外投票的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/pennsylvania-judge-joins-rebuff-of-gop-on-overseas-voting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党在最近输掉了三起诉讼，这些诉讼质疑战场州如何处理居住在海外的美国公民的投票权，一名密歇根州法官严厉谴责了共和党在 11 月 5 日大选前“在最后一刻试图剥夺美国人的选举权”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/pennsylvania-judge-joins-rebuff-of-gop-on-overseas-voting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报告称欧盟必须加强情报联系以应对威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/eu-must-boost-intelligence-ties-to-counter-threats-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项建议撤销了欧盟情报机构的初步计划，称欧盟应该与成员国的间谍机构合作，创建一个集团层面的合作平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/eu-must-boost-intelligence-ties-to-counter-threats-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 11:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列讨论以美国为首的新协议以结束真主党冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/israel-eyes-deal-to-end-lebanon-combat-after-weakening-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在评估真主党武装分子的火箭弹库已基本耗尽或被摧毁后，以色列正在考虑接受由美国主导的一项协议，以结束黎巴嫩冲突并将真主党武装分子撤出以色列边境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/israel-eyes-deal-to-end-lebanon-combat-after-weakening-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:51:48 GMT</pubDate>
